&lt;p&gt;You have prior product management experience and deep familiarity with sanctions compliance and risk intelligence products. You understand the complexity of building products for regulated users who need to move quickly, trust the information presented to them, and explain their decisions to internal stakeholders and regulators. You are excited to help Quantifind expand into new product areas and shape the initial product offering. You bring sanctions domain expertise, understand the realities of screening and investigation workflows and know where existing tools fall short. You know how to make clear prioritization tradeoffs to define a practical MVP to solve our customers’ most pressing problems. You are drawn to this role because you want the opportunity to define the product offering and make foundational decisions.&lt;/p&gt;
