&lt;p&gt;You bring a balance of technical discipline and marketing awareness, with the ability to work effectively within modern CMS and visual development environments. While you understand underlying web technologies, your strength lies in applying that knowledge to build, manage, and optimize within platforms like Webflow or WordPress, where speed, structure, and scalability matter.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You think critically about how pages perform, how users navigate the site, how data is captured, and how incremental improvements affect conversion, and you are comfortable owning both execution and optimization: building, testing, refining, and maintaining a site that is reliable, performant, and continuously improving.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Quantifind is the leader in AI-driven risk intelligence, helping financial institutions and government agencies detect and disrupt financial crime and national security threats. Our platform delivers accurate, scalable, and explainable intelligence across KYC, sanctions, payments, and investigations workflows.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As we scale, our website is a critical part of how we engage the market, communicate value, and generate demand.&lt;/p&gt;
