&lt;li&gt;Data-driven mindset with a focus on measurable outcomes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong project management and prioritization skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work cross-functionally and influence stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
